.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個心當時係被撕裂"},{"pid":"8e5c3e973486794890621841eca617f9613c6903","tid":81211,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拍左2年半 4定5個月放底 <br />\n識多d人 世界很大 自我心態最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇試過死頂之後崩潰左<br />\n崩潰完之後會唔會好得快左？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭1個月成日諗住佢<br />\n不過一定要有個: 我好想放低既意志 <br />\n跟住搵人傾<br />\n一定要搵d屌得醒你既人 唔好搵d比on9意見既人 eg唔好唔開心啦<br />\n喊左2次狗屎咁 醒醒地<br />\n加上係咁睇高登分手post 明分手係自然既事<br />\n明大家係唔適合先會分手<br />\n<br />\n同埋玩左soc 識左好多人<br />\n發覺ex唔係有咁特別 珍惜下自己仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係因為崩潰而醒 而係成長<br />\n知自己都有唔好要去改"},{"pid":"65feb65ce1a3374657c8d7f9b00c525a4710014e","tid":81211,"uid":39046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拍左2年半 4定5個月放底 <br />\n識多d人 世界很大 自我心態最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但你個名唔似放低曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n名唔關ex事 而角色你調轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db1de8cea2f250d235732fd4c9ff24ecd6cea49","tid":81211,"uid":58070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想聽下女仔經歷<br />\n<br />\n你地點樣去重新接受第二個？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n以為自己放低左同左第二個一齊 兩個都對我好好 超級錫我 但係兩個分手原因都係話自己唔夠好 到底我有咩問題導致兩次分手都係呢個原因<br />\n<br />\n利申佢地都成日話我多兵 關事？求巴打解合 我唸起兩個其中一個都會喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8abccf1aca680fe02a8238db95757de1b31c2a","tid":81211,"uid":68986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T0