,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"4d92b0b530b380b55f4dfd62fa58c83b7f9d47a7","tid":81211,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T17:47:51.000Z","msg":"望住中意緊既人忘記唔到前度仲要咁痛苦真係好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3c40ab50111d7adf66c4e0657e6db3b6679f29","tid":81211,"uid":22084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心態好重要<br />\n有時唔需要刻意去做<br />\n慢慢你都要放手<br />\n有d 人離開左，記住感覺只會令人更痛苦<br />\n<br />\n利：拍拖3 年，分左年幾，用依年幾去感悟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係拍左三年 未分 但黎緊星期四出黎和平分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdf3c9a1d2ce2dce9af8f72aa60f730a5edc165","tid":81211,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T19:27:20.000Z","msg":"掟去資源回收筒"},{"pid":"d11c3f43b22d1bcc57418cc91f4a3474adaa64fa","tid":81211,"uid":10733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T20:45:25.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗特登放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個容器咁大 呢d咁少份量既事都唔會佔好多位姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e44159d26d16e1e98776cd693b8c112f4caafc","tid":81211,"uid":77148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T21:08:17.000Z","msg":"拍左十幾次拖，每次分手後都有種放下心頭大石自由自在既感覺，諗反轉頭其實咁多個都唔係我真正鐘意，真正有心跳感覺個三位我都只能遠處欣賞，默默係身邊守護<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3a31e9214c236e76dfea7140f21c037b08ee81","tid":81211,"uid":16808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T21:17:30.000Z","msg":"等時間慢慢過 <br />\n不停做野等自己少d時間去諗<br />\n不斷提自己放只會更加放唔到<br />\n<br />\n初戀拍左年幾 <br />\n差唔多兩年都未完全放低晒"},{"pid":"f8e3fb0ab6aec5ae399dfc83264fe7bd6c6a5035","tid":81211,"uid":27